{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01FXREYXff2BYg8wjFxjbJ7x","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"`@solana/wallet-adapter-react` is a dependency of the `wallet` package but not the platform app. The platform app imports from `@rng-utopia/wallet/hooks`, so it doesn't directly depend on the adapter. But `CoinflipContext.tsx` now directly imports from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`. I need to add it as a dependency of the platform app, or restructure the import.\n\nActually, the cleaner approach is to re-export `useConnection` from the wallet package so consumers don't need a direct dependency on `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`. Let me check what the wallet package exports."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":362,"cache_read_input_tokens":62041,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":362},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"dc9fbb5c-f0ae-42eb-8036-00379cf160bf","uuid":"7a4d1936-e21e-4eae-ae71-803fb94852c2"}
